###
#
# 1.9.20/2.0.0-rc1 release
#
###

2011-08-21 12:03  owes

	* updates/1.9.20/information.xml: Finish update information

2011-08-20 09:10  owes

	* langs/de_DE/ipcop.po, langs/list_progress: Updates from language
	  DB.

2011-08-19 07:34  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/logconfig.cgi: Change order of options to make log
	  archive more 'prominent'.

2011-08-19 07:31  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/logproxy.cgi: Modify the searching through logfiles
	  to use the date in logrotated filenames.

2011-08-19 07:09  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/proxy.cgi: Change path etc. for squidGuard (URL
	  filter).

2011-08-19 07:07  owes

	* updates/1.9.20/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.20: logrotate.conf is a
	  symlink, should not be overwritten by the update.

2011-08-19 07:03  owes

	* src/misc-progs/setaliases.c: Remove unused variable. Slightly
	  improve comment.

2011-08-18 18:00  owes

	* src/misc-progs/restartsyslogd.c: Only modify /etc/logrotate.conf
	  when needed.

2011-08-18 14:32  owes

	* src/installer/hardware.c: Add USB_CLASS_WIRELESS as potential
	  network card. Android device with tethering via USB identifies
	  itself with that class.

2011-08-18 14:30  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/logfirewall.cgi, html/cgi-bin/logsystem.cgi: Modify
	  the searching through logfiles to use the date in logrotated
	  filenames.

2011-08-18 13:46  owes

	* config/logrotate/logrotate.conf.FLASH,
	  config/logrotate/logrotate.conf.HDD,
	  config/logrotate/logrotate.d/apache2,
	  config/logrotate/logrotate.d/squid,
	  config/rootfiles/common/logrotate, lfs/logrotate,
	  updates/1.9.20/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.20,
	  updates/1.9.20/information.xml: Upgrade logrotate to 3.8.0,
	  change download URL from Debian to upstream.
	  Change rotation to daily for both Flash and HDD and use date in
	  rotated files.

