	* lfs/tzdata: Add the URL where to found old releases

2011-08-06 13:15  gespinasse

	* lfs/perl: Use the perlish way : use debian patchlevel so applied
	  patches appear on perl -V
	  For this, apply patchlevel patch and remove from patchlevel.h the
	  non-applied patch lines
	  
	  I haven't checked for post 1.9.19 changes on perl due to new
	  patching. I would need rebuilding 1.9.19 on this machine before
	  to run check_files.
	  
	  Enhance the comments concerning perl patching

