2011-08-02 18:27  eoberlander

	* src/scripts/makegraphs, updates/1.9.20/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.20,
	  updates/1.9.20/information.xml: Proposed fix for SF Bug 3000712 -
	  Spike in graph data at boot up. Noted that it only happens on
	  warm reboots. Currently requires existing RRDs to be replaced.

