2011-07-06 20:23  gespinasse

	* lfs/ccache: Upgrade ccache to 3.1.5
	  Nothing change on log (except in ccache-stats.log
	  
	  Upgrade will invalidate some cache signatures, and particulary
	  slow down the kernel until the next rebuild
	  
	  New version change some stats result :
	  - solve most of 'unsupported compiler option'
	  - increase 'cache hit (preprocessed)' and decrease 'cache hit
	  (direct)' from the same amount
	  
	  I will upgrade the toolchain package ref when gcc and make
	  upgrade have been commited.

