2011-02-18 13:48  gespinasse

	* lfs/coreutils: Fix sparse-to-pipe that may fail due to a race.
	  This happen only in one machine in the 4 I tested for unclear
	  reason (maybe 2.6.26 debian kernel).
	  Upstream fix is to add a wait.
	  
	  As I am there, add -j 1 for the tests
	  Add -k for non-root test, so tests continue in case of first
	  failure

