2010-12-23 07:35  owes

	* src/misc-progs/setfwrules.c: Add --emergency command line option.
	  setfwrules --emergency will (re)enable Admin access for GREEN and
	  remove MAC filter. This gives Admin access for GUI and SSH from
	  GREEN in case Admin has locked himself out.
	  Needs documentation.

