	* src/patches/gcc-4.4.5_fortify-source-1.patch,
	  src/patches/gcc-4.4.5_fpie-1.patch,
	  src/patches/gcc-4.4.5_fstack-protector-1.patch: Add 3 gcc patches
	  from HLFS, useful to create/verify gcc specs file

2010-12-22 09:03  owes

	* lfs/util-linux-ng: Make sure util-linux-ng build picks up -fPIE
	  -pie

2010-12-22 06:51  gespinasse

	* lfs/stage2: Use the toolchain bump opportunity to change stty
	  symlink
	  
	  Since I use a sed on expect compilation like in DIY to remove the
	  hardcoded path for stty, we do not need to create the stty
	  symlink
	  
	  stty from tools will be used first until the one from chroot is
	  compiled
	  
	  That will remove one less cheat in coreutils rootfiles list

2010-12-21 22:20  owes

	* lfs/initramfs: There are 1 or 2 D_TEXTREL fatal warnings in
	  mklibs. Until we find and fix those, ignore the warnings.

2010-12-21 22:18  owes

	* lfs/sysfsutils: Add with-pic to sysfsutils configure

2010-12-21 22:17  owes

	* lfs/memtest,
	  src/patches/memtest86+-4.10_compile-with-no-pie.patch: Compile
	  parts of memtest without pie (and friends) to avoid build
	  problems.

2010-12-21 22:15  owes

	* lfs/gnupg: Make sure gnupg build picks up -fPIE -pie

2010-12-21 22:14  owes

	* config/rootfiles/common/capi4k-utils,
	  config/rootfiles/common/capi4k-utils_SKIP, make.sh: Disable
	  capi4k-utils until we fix build problem

2010-12-21 22:12  owes

	* lfs/gcc, lfs/glibc, make.sh: Redo our hardening. Apart from gnupg
	  there are no more TEXTREL files left.
	  Hardening is done slightly different compared with HLFS. Using a
	  hardened toolchain is not needed for our case, as we replace all
	  files later and we only use toolchain once.
	  
	  Bump toolchainversion to make sure everybody builds new one.
	  Remove hardening from CFLAGS and readd via gcc specs file.
	  Make sure glibc detects PIC capable compiler
	  (libc_cv_pic_default).
	  Build glibc in 2 stages for library and programs with different
	  hardening settings.
	  Add 'hardened' specs file at the end of gcc in stage base.

2010-12-21 22:01  owes

	* lfs/e2fsprogs: Remove comment for uuidd, make sure PIC is used
	  for building

2010-12-21 21:59  owes

	* lfs/coreutils: Make sure we do not build doc and mapage, as that
	  causes lots of trouble

