	* doc/How-to-make-update: Document correct location of patch files
	  on SF

2010-03-12 18:30  gespinasse

	* lfs/apache: Always build apache with include apr lib.
	  In case of apache upgrade, previous apr would have been used
	  So new lib would miss on cdrom.
	  
	  thank at Guenter to understand and fix that

