	  build-rdepend show no code that depend on gmp
	  gmp is build to late for gcc and coreutils
	  But more change are needed to be able to compile gmp earlier.
	  At least m4 should be added to the toolchain.
	  
	  openswan use it during compilation (search for lgmp)
	  Is a restart of openswan somewhere needed to use the new lib?

