2010-02-26 22:12  gespinasse

	* lfs/udev: build udev in a reliable manner
	  
	  When a patch change configure.ac, configure.in, a race may occure
	  with timestamp
	  
	  Before running autoreconf
	  
	  for i in `seq 1 10`; do (./make.sh build | grep udev; rm -f log_i
	  486/02_base/udev* );done
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 23 ] [ FAIL ]
	  ERROR: Building udev [ FAIL ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 24 ] [ FAIL ]
	  ERROR: Building udev [ FAIL ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 27 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 23 ] [ FAIL ]
	  ERROR: Building udev [ FAIL ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 23 ] [ FAIL ]
	  ERROR: Building udev [ FAIL ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 26 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 27 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 24 ] [ FAIL ]
	  ERROR: Building udev [ FAIL ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 26 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 26 ] [ DONE ]
	  
	  After autoreconf added
	  for i in `seq 1 10`; do (./make.sh build | grep udev; rm -f
	  log_i486/02_base/udev* );done
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 23 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 23 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]
	  udev [ 146 ] [ 22 ] [ DONE ]

2010-02-26 17:38  owes

	* config/rootfiles/common/openssl, lfs/openssl,
