	* html/cgi-bin/openvpn.cgi, updates/1.9.13/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.13:
	  When configuring the OpenVPN net something like 10.0.10.0/24 is
	  accepted as valid, but the server.conf wants 10.0.10.0
	  255.255.255.0
	  Make sure we always write .conf properly, regardless of notation
	  used by admin.

