	  Remove no longer needed/valid configuration lines from
	  firewall/policy

2010-02-13 10:56  owes

	* lfs/initramfs, make.sh: If we skip floppy images, we do not need
	  mini-initramfs and can skip building klibc.
	  Helpfull as klibc is not buildable on newer kernels.
	  
	  We may need to reconsider if we really want to continue
	  supporting floppy based installation.

