	* updates/1.9.12/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.12: Add rc.conexantpciadsl into
	  upgrade package

2010-02-12 16:31  gespinasse

	* src/rc.d/rc.conexantpciadsl: Remove the match on 14f1 only, it
	  may match a tulip card
	  Fixes for proc pci on 2.6 and cat is not needed to grep
	  
	  My Yukon card does not yet work.
	  I have to spend a bit more time on this.
	  Is yukon firmware required like I do on 2.4?
	  If no, firmware.hex trick and symlink is not needed

