2009-12-18 11:57  owes

	* html/cgi-bin/ipsec.cgi, src/libs/vpn-functions.pl,
	  updates/1.9.11/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.11: Drop ipsec interface for
	  Green, reshuffle ipsec interface assignment. The way we currently
	  build and/or use IPsec we only have ipsec0 and ipsec1 (no more
	  interfaces). Not sure why that happens.
	  
	  We should also (seriously) consider dropping IPsec for Orange.

