2009-12-14 17:01  owes

	* lfs/mdadm, src/installer/partition.c,
	  updates/1.9.11/ROOTFILES.i486-1.9.11,
	  updates/1.9.11/information.xml: Upgrade mdadm to 3.1.1
	  mdadm now uses metadata v1.1 as default when creating arrays,
	  which does not seem to work with extlinux (or MBR). So use
	  metadata v0.9.

