	  Upgrade kernel to 2.6.27.41 and enable CONFIG_USB_HIDDEV (needed
	  for APC UPS).
	  Bump our kernel version to 2.6.27-3, this is not strictly needed
	  as the changes are minimal (I think), still it is a good idea as
	  we need to test kernel upgrade sooner or later.

